OL,3,CGerry Kelly will not contest next
OL,4,CStormont election
OL,6,FThe Sinn Fein MLA Gerry Kelly has
OL,7,Fannounced he will not contest the next
OL,8,FStormont election.
OL,10,FMr Kelly has been an elected
OL,11,Frepresentative in north Belfast since
OL,12,F1998.
OL,14,FHe will continue as an MLA until the
OL,15,Fassembly elections which are due by
OL,16,FMay 2027.
OL,18,FThe party said they are currently "in
OL,19,Fthe process of candidate selection in
OL,20,Fa number of constituencies".
