OL,3,CGerry Kelly will not contest next
OL,4,CStormont election
OL,6,FMr Kelly said it was "the greatest
OL,7,Fhonour" to serve the people of north
OL,8,FBelfast.
OL,10,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill
OL,11,Fthanked him for his "decades of
OL,12,Fdedicated service and commitment to
OL,13,FIrish unity".
